*    Write program to convert temperature from degree centigrade to Fahrenheit
*    Output:
*    enter temp in centigrade: 32
*    temp in Fahrenheit=89.59998
*    [hint] ğ¹ğ‘â„ğ‘Ÿğ‘’ğ‘›â„ğ‘’ğ‘–ğ‘¡ = 1.8âˆ— ğ‘ğ‘’ğ‘›ğ‘¡ğ‘–ğ‘”ğ‘Ÿğ‘ğ‘‘ğ‘’ + 32
*
